msgstr ""
"这份指南是我学习 `OpenNFT <https://www.opennft.org>`_ 时的笔记，不是 `官方指南 "
"<https://opennft.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html>`_ ，也不是教程，而是我学习 "
"OpenNFT 时的笔记。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:10 d88b066fe3104246b1748a38e37a8982
msgid "Summary of the paper"
msgstr "论文摘要"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:12 f3a9a5593efe41cf99f77e72d233bac6
msgid ""
"This section of the notebook provides a summary of the paper titled "
"`\"OpenNFT: An open-source Python/Matlab framework for real-time fMRI "
"neurofeedback training based on activity, connectivity and multivariate "
"pattern analysis\" "
"<http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.neuroimage.2017.06.039>`_."
msgstr "这一段笔记提供了一篇论文的摘要，标题为 `\"OpenNFT: An open-source Python/Matlab framework for real-time fMRI neurofeedback training based on activity, connectivity and multivariate pattern analysis\" <http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.neuroimage.2017.06.039>`_ 。

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:15 8d50b5abc35847979f68ea7bcc9741fe
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介绍"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:17 745b91dfb1094369a93f60ac324d4b72
msgid ""
"The motivation of the paper is to leverage **neurofeedback** to help "
"participants learn **voluntary control** over their own brain activity "
"and connectivity via **operant conditioning**. The superiority of such "
"approach lies in the fact that it is **drug free**, **non-invasive**, and"
" **effective** in treating a variety of diseases."
msgstr "这篇文章的动机是利用 **神经反馈** 帮助参与者通过 **操作性条件反射** 学习对自己的大脑活动和连接性进行 **自主控制** 。这种方法的优越性在于它是 **无药物** 、 **非侵入性** 的，而且在治疗各种疾病方面是 **有效的** 。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:20 bf38994f53d048f6978c570e2fce5ee2
msgid ""
"The authors compares **neurofeedback based on rt-fMRI** to **conventional"
" neurofeedback study**."
msgstr "作者将 **基于实时功能磁共振成像的神经反馈** 与 **传统的神经反馈研究** 进行了比较。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:22 093c32e5f1d54463ad3e3e4b2107fa27
msgid "Conventional neurofeedback study"
msgstr "传统的神经反馈研究"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:24 9a90453d8c33421c9f1ffa8f36b09bdf
msgid "Performance of the participant not evaluated in real-time"
msgstr "参与者的表现没有实时评估"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:25 c3b4fcaf79ce410aa70dd66981da83f2
msgid "Challenging to evaluate behavioral/therapeutic effect"
msgstr "难以评估行为/治疗效果"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:26 26409082e5db4813ab1a4ef754555a6e
msgid "Range from single-day session to long session over several days"
msgstr "持续时间从单日到几天"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:28 9f4a227d32df4c52b0a7942d5fc51f74
msgid "Neurofeedback based on rt-fMRI"
msgstr "基于实时功能磁共振成像的神经反馈"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:30 d418160c2bb5468097237daad0d8ee93
msgid "Demands high-performance computer"
msgstr "需要高性能计算机"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:31 6440e06819b543f9931a60d74309ed47
msgid "Lacks open-source GUI-based framework"
msgstr "缺乏开源的基于图形用户界面的框架"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:33 fab88ea8e7964b389ca99942c89bae99
msgid ""
"And OpenNFT falls under the category of **neurofeedback based on rt-"
"fMRI**."
msgstr "而 OpenNFT 属于 **基于实时功能磁共振成像的神经反馈** 。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:36 076ce91647f64843a3e334637ee2f837
msgid "Methods"
msgstr "方法"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:38 11aefc06ad4944718522f05468960004
msgid "Neurofeedback data acquisition and transfer"
msgstr "神经反馈数据采集和传输"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:40 9a8d4bb141ba49be97572e189cd07432
msgid ""
"A **data analysis workstation** (where OpenNFT is installed) is added to "
"the same network as the MR scanner and reconstruction console."
msgstr "一个 **数据分析工作站** (安装了 OpenNFT) 被添加到与 MR 扫描仪和重建控制台相同的网络中。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:42 4830266798ef49e68ebc8f9ba4cb03f2
msgid ""
"MR hardware and software export acquired and reconstructed data to a "
"shared folder."
msgstr "MR 硬件和软件将采集和重建的数据导出到一个共享文件夹。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:43 43e2bb19d66f4a188811b59083203320
msgid "Data analysis workstation access the exported data via **TCP/IP**."
msgstr "数据分析工作站通过 **TCP/IP** 访问导出的数据。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:45 06bd62a1b8b84f138f46af1a90e2c260
msgid "Timing and synchronization"
msgstr "时间和同步"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:47 5a4631c54361434f9ddf1d3a7586c76b
msgid "Data preprocessing"
msgstr "数据预处理"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:49 e48c8c4d2bae4411b4b4efa0d47b1faa
msgid ""
"If precautions are not taken against movement, **spatial alignment** and "
"**reslicing** (via SPM12) are recommended."
msgstr "如果没有采取措施防止头部移动，建议使用 **空间对齐** 和 **重采样** (通过 SPM12)。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:51 44924e092bc34578ad02618c829a47d0
msgid "Data processing"
msgstr "数据处理"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:53 ec01bbc9094a45f58af680e1315f8726
msgid ""
"**Incremental GLM (iGLM)** is used to estimate **whole-brian activation "
"maps** which is displayed in real-time."
msgstr " **增量广义线性模型 (iGLM)** 用于估计 **全脑激活图** ，并实时显示。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:54 0488fd16a0c14b63879e5a40087a14d9
msgid ""
"**Cumulative GLM** is used to correct for **linear drift** and **head "
"motions**."
msgstr " **累积广义线性模型** 用于校正 **线性漂移** 和 **头部运动**。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:55 0a47863fe43447029a2180d61d47177d
msgid ""
"**Low-pass Kalman filter** extracts **desired signal** and discards "
"**high-frequency noise**."
msgstr " **低通卡尔曼滤波器** 提取 **信号** 并丢弃 **高频噪声**。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:56 55641c041d5841b7b480d33971742436
msgid ""
"**First-order autoregressive model (AR(1))** applied on **all voxels' "
"time-series** **prior to estimation of the GLM** is used account for "
"serial correlations in fMRI data due to **non-neurophysiological "
"fluctuations** and **non-modeled neuronal activity**."
msgstr " **一阶自回归模型 (AR(1))** 应用于 **所有体素的时间序列** ，用于估计 GLM 之前，用于解释 fMRI 数据中由于 **非神经生理波动** 和 **非模拟的神经元活动** 而产生的序列相关性。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:57 5f1f842f6a5d423dabf2a7a84b63280f
msgid "**Dynamic ROI estimation**."
msgstr "**动态 ROI 估计**。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:59 b561fcc5deaa46ed96c21b0bb18bf872
msgid "Feedback estimation"
msgstr "反馈估计"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:61 51001a08f2004e0fa54e6ae3e7e781a7
msgid ""
"Constantly displayed (continuous) and periodically displayed "
"(intermittent) **activation-based** feedbacks"
msgstr "持续显示 (连续) 和周期显示 (间歇) **基于激活** 的反馈"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:63 c77bf1a63d6c4f6b96cb3552db99dc02
