"spatial-temporal data sample within the ROI, and"
msgstr "从 ROI 内的空间-时间数据样本中获得平均值、加权平均值或特征向量估计，以及"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:68 5b23652aa424497482702e409190faea
msgid ""
"Adaptively scaling (normalizing) the time-series (to prevent confusion "
"for the participants)."
msgstr "自适应地缩放 (归一化) 时间序列 (以防止参与者混淆)。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:70 b480f0f1ad0744a98f69d04f3e8e4871
msgid "Intermittent effective **connectivity** feedback"
msgstr "间歇性的有效 **连接** 反馈"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:72 fe80ebe9f7a74701a0140ca02a6cff01
msgid "Connectivity can estimated as:"
msgstr "连接可以估计为："

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:74 f093b638702a43ae93ad1aefe71b876b
msgid ""
"Temporal correlation (using **Pearson correlation coefficient** "
"estimation) between two time-series, and"
msgstr "两个时间序列之间的时间相关性 (使用 **Pearson 相关系数** 估计)，以及"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:75 f093b638702a43ae93ad1aefe71b876b
msgid ""
"Functional connectivity networks using **real-time Smooth Incremental "
"Graphical Lasso (rt-SINGLE)**."
msgstr "使用 **实时平滑增量图形 Lasso (rt-SINGLE)** 的功能连接网络。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:77 0b49a457942d42de9cf2b917df3825bf
msgid ""
"Dynamic causal modeling (DCM) can also be used to estimate effective "
"connectivity."
msgstr "动态因果建模 (DCM) 也可以用来估计有效连接。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:79 f4d4496f1d5144c6892d4d291bea1ab5
msgid "Continuous **classification-based** feedback"
msgstr "连续的 **基于分类** 的反馈"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:81 d54f3614e19d461ebdb1a6a0b838c8f1
msgid ""
"A **supporting vector machine (SVM) classifier** is trained prior to "
"neurofeedback run to discriminate between two attention states."
msgstr "在神经反馈运行之前，训练一个 **支持向量机 (SVM) 分类器** ，以区分两种注意状态。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:82 9af12bd4a85a40b2b8c93698ca2eeaa3
msgid ""
"Accuracy of classification is determined using **n-fold cross "
"validation**."
msgstr "使用 **n 折交叉验证** 确定分类的准确性。"

#: ../../source/Intro.rst:83 039e34f371c04ba8b8e5ab692fc1af04
msgid "The trained classifier is used to provide neurofeedback."
msgstr "训练好的分类器用于提供神经反馈。"

